1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper is focused on face detection and proposes a new approach to enrich feature maps using density map estimation. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new module inspired by recent crowd counting/density estimation techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a feature enrichment module to improve the accuracy of detecting smaller faces. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper evaluates the proposed approach on different datasets such as WIDER, FDDB and Pascal-Faces. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the least likely category as the paper does not focus on security or cryptography.
